Name: Frequency of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' compared to the total number of declarations submitted.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' followed by 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in relation to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'.
Metric: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' activities for cases where activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all rejections.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity LIKE 'Declaration REJECTED by %'"}

Name: Frequency of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in variants involving 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'.
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' for cases where activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' that lead to a new submission by the same employee within a month.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity == 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' AND time:timestamp <= '1 month'"}

Name: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' with amounts above 100 euros.
Metric: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' activities > 100 where ma is the last value of case:Amount

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' by 'STAFF MEMBER' compared to 'SYSTEM'.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' per year.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'total', 'group_by': 'year'}

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in the process flow before 'Request Payment'.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all 'Request Payment'

Name: Ratio of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' over 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'ratio', 'filter': "activity == 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'"}

Name: Number of times 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' is the final activity in a case.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'aggregation': 'total', 'filter': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' AND activity == LAST_ACTIVITY"}

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in cases with a budget number different from budget 86566.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in cases with an amount higher than the average case amount.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'total', 'filter': 'case:Amount > AVERAGE(case:Amount)'}

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in cases that involve travel expense claims for domestic trips.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all cases
